column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.type, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s.zErr, zWarning, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, pz.z As Photo_Z, pz.zErr AS Photo_Err FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID = p.objid
